# Team C: Gym Class Bad
 

When I went to Talcott I did not hate gym class in a small way. I hated it in a big way.  In a deep and broad way, an existential hatred that consumed by being. I wanted to destroy not just any one activity or teacher but the concept of gym class. I was an opponent of it.

Team C was a systemic attack on gym class. I organized it.  The concept was that gym class has two teams.  We formed a third which existed as a random salting of elements on both teams.  At a completely randomly chosen time